video.title: Power Rangers Samurai
video.synopsis: A new generation of Power Rangers must master the Symbols of Samurai Power, which give them control over the Earth's elements to battle dark forces.

episodes.synopsis: As invasions from the Netherworld increase, the Red Ranger unites a new team of Samurai Rangers to meet the rising threat.
episodes.title: Origins: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: As the teens continue their transition into their new secret lives as Samurai Rangers, Emily reveals a surprising truth about herself.
episodes.title: Origins: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: Mike figures out the hard way what it means to be a Samurai Ranger after a Nighlok attacks him and his friends.
episodes.title: The Team Unites

episodes.synopsis: The Rangers step in when a devious Nighlok tricks a young boy into giving up on his baseball dreams.
episodes.title: Deal with a Nighlok

episodes.synopsis: Struggling to master a secret power disc, Jayden chooses not to go with the others to an amusement park, where the team encounters an evil Nighlok.
episodes.title: Day Off

episodes.synopsis: When a Nighlok who uses insults as a physical weapon attacks the Rangers, only Emily is unaffected.
episodes.title: Sticks & Stones

episodes.synopsis: Kevin is assigned the crucial task of catching the elusive SwordfishZord in order to save the other Rangers, who have been incapacitated a Nighlok.
episodes.title: A Fish Out of Water

episodes.synopsis: Dayu crosses into the mortal world to cause misery by kidnapping brides on their wedding day.
episodes.title: There Go the Brides

episodes.synopsis: A Nighlok uses mind-control powers to force Kevin to fight against his fellow Rangers.
episodes.title: I've Got a Spell on Blue

episodes.synopsis: After Mike goes rogue in battle, Mentor takes Mike's Samuraizer away until he learns a deeper lesson about the nature of the Green Ranger's power.
episodes.title: Forest for the Trees

episodes.synopsis: A Nighlok is sent to stop the Red Ranger from using his special power to seal Master Xandred in the Netherworld forever.
episodes.title: Test of the Leader

episodes.synopsis: Jayden leaves the Shiba house hoping to keep the other Rangers out of harm's way -- until a powerful Nighlok attacks.
episodes.title: Jayden's Challenge

episodes.synopsis: A traveling fisherman named Antonio arrives and claims to be the sixth Samurai Ranger.
episodes.title: Unexpected Arrival

episodes.synopsis: Jayden's childhood friend and self-made Samurai Antonio struggles to be accepted by the team as the Gold Ranger.
episodes.title: Room for One More

episodes.synopsis: As Antonio attempts to gain Kevin's respect as a true Samurai, Octoroo devises a plan to create a stronger portal between the Netherworld and Earth.
episodes.title: The Blue and the Gold

episodes.synopsis: The Rangers must defeat the evil Splitface, who steals people's spirits -- including the Yellow Ranger's -- before sending them into an eternal sleep.
episodes.title: Team Spirit

episodes.synopsis: Jayden is poisoned by Octoroo during his attempt to discover the Red Ranger's sealing symbol, which can lock away Master Xandred forever.
episodes.title: The Tengen Gate

episodes.synopsis: With Jayden kidnapped by Deker, the other Rangers must summon the strength to fight a mutant Nighlok without their leader.
episodes.title: Boxed In

episodes.synopsis: When the Gold and Pink Ranger fall under the spell of a dream-inducing Nighlok, the other Rangers must enter the Dream World to save them.
episodes.title: Broken Dreams

episodes.synopsis: The Rangers try to finish off the dream monster Rhinosnorus while Jayden and Deker finally face off in their ultimate duel.
episodes.title: The Ultimate Duel
